msgstr "1400:The NewGen killer, for example, was surely going to be caught before too long. Then they'd spend the next few decades in prison before finally being given the death penalty.[%p]"

msgid "1500:僕はその犯人にこう言ってやりたいね。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:I knew exactly what I wanted to say to them.[%p]"

msgid "1600:――あーあ、妄想だけで済ませとけばよかったのに。[%p]"
