msgstr "2400:I could feel the humidity clinging to my skin. If I hadn't known better, I would've assumed it had just rained. The air felt... sticky.[%p]"

msgid "2500:音が――[linebreak]なにかを引きずっているかのような音が、かすかに聞こえてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "2500:And then the sound... I could hear a faint sound, like something dragging.[%p]"

msgid "2600:僕は足を止めて、耳を澄ませた。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:I stopped to listen.[%p]"

msgid "2700:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "2700:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "2800:その音は、僕の立つ場所から左側へと折れている狭そうな路地の奥から聞こえてきている……そんな気がした。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:The sound was coming from the back of a small alley on my left... at least, as near as I could tell.[%p]"

msgid "2900:街路灯はなくて、周囲の家の明かりも消えていた。[%p]"
