msgid "10900:血と糞尿を垂れ流して地面に横たわっているそれから、僕は慌てて目をそらす。[%p]"
msgstr "10900:Blood, shit, and piss were coming out of its body as it lay there on the road. I quickly turned away.[%p]"

msgid "11000:気持ち悪さでゾワゾワと鳥肌が立ち、その場で踵を返した。[%p]"
msgstr "11000:The disgusting sight gave me goosebumps. I turned around to leave.[%p]"

msgid "11100:そこにも、猫がいた。[linebreak]生きている、黒猫。[linebreak]闇の中に浮かび上がる黄金の瞳が、僕を見つめていた。[%p]"
msgstr "11100:There was another cat there. This one was alive. Its golden eyes were clearly visible in the darkness. They were staring at me.[%p]"

msgid "11200:[name]拓巳[line]「……な、なん、だよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "11200:[name]拓巳[line]W-What do you want?[%p]"

msgid "11300:僕が声を出すと、猫は素早い身のこなしで物陰へと姿を消す。[linebreak]なんだかイヤな感じだった。[%p]"
msgstr "11300:The cat quickly vanished behind a nearby object. Something about that thing gave me the creeps.[%p]"

msgid "11400:さっさとコンビニへ行こう。でもこの道は使えない。猫の死体があるから通れない。迂回するしかなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "11400:I wanted to hurry to the convenience store, but I couldn't use this route. I wasn't going past that dead cat. I'd have to go around another way.[%p]"

msgid "11500:……歩き出そうとして、気付く。[linebreak]さっきから、妙な音が聞こえているような……[%p]"
msgstr "11500:I started walking, and then I realized something.[%p]"

msgid "11600:僕はゴクリと息を呑んでから、じっと耳を澄ました。[%p]"
msgstr "11600:For a while now, I'd been hearing a strange sound. I gulped and listened closer to hear what it was.[%p]"

msgid "11700:[name]拓巳[line]「………………最悪だ」[%p]"
msgstr "11700:[name]拓巳[line]… Yuck.[%p]"

msgid "11800:僕はパソコンモニタの前に座っている。[%p]"
msgstr "11800:I was sitting in front of my computer monitor.[%p]"

msgid "11900:のどの渇きを潤すために、コーラを口の中に流し込んで、リクライニングシートの上でため息をついた。[%p]"
msgstr "11900:I gulped down some soda and sighed in my reclining chair.[%p]"

msgid "12000:イヤな妄想をしちゃったよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "12000:That delusion was just awful.[%p]"

msgid "12100:昨日から今日にかけて、いろいろとグロい話ばっかり聞かされてたせいだ。[%p]"
msgstr "12100:It was probably because of all the disgusting things I'd been hearing about since yesterday.[%p]"

msgid "12200:僕は周囲に影響されて、よく自分でも思ってもみないような妄想をしちゃうことがあった。たいていは、自分の妄想にもかかわらずすごくイヤな気分になるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "12200:Sometimes I'd have delusions like these, things I could never come up with on my own. It usually happened when I was being influenced by something going on around me. Usually they were really nasty, disgusting things.[%p]"

msgid "12300:想像力がありすぎるのかな、僕って。[%p]"
msgstr "12300:Maybe I just had too vivid an imagination.[%p]"

msgid "12400:断片的な情報しかないときほど、そういう妄想が頭の中に浮かんでくる確率が高い。[linebreak]あまりの怖さに悲鳴を上げちゃったりもする。[%p]"
msgstr "12400:The less I understood about something, the more likely it was to show up in my delusions. Sometimes I got so scared, I'd scream.[%p]"

msgid "12500:ベースでならともかく、学校とか、今僕がいるこのネットカフェみたいな場所でそんなマネをしたら、目もあてられない。[%p]"
msgstr "12500:It was one thing to do that in the Base, but at school, or even in a net café like the one I was in now, that was an absolute no-no.[%p]"

msgid "12600:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ、僕は、引きこもりじゃ――」[%p]"
msgstr "12600:[name]拓巳[line]I-I'm not a hikikomori...[%p]"

msgid "12700:三住くんのあまりの言いように、抗議の声を上げようとした。[%p]"
msgstr "12700:I tried to protest.[%p]"

msgid "12800:でもそれを言うことで彼に嫌われていじめられたりしたらどうしよう、と思うと、結局言葉を呑み込むしかない。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:But I worried that he might hate me, or try to bully me, and just gulped down my words.[%p]"

msgid "12900:僕は唇を噛んで、三住くんから顔をそむけた。[linebreak]何気なく視線をさまよわせ、黒板に書いてある文字をぼんやりと眺める。[%p]"
msgstr "12900:I bit my lip and looked away from him. I found myself looking around the room, and saw something written on the blackboard.[%p]"

msgid "13000:最初は――[linebreak]そこになんて書いてあるのかに興味はなかった。ただ“文字が描かれている”としか認識していなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "13000:At first... I didn't really care what it was. All I noticed was that there was some writing there.[%p]"

msgid "13100:でも眺めているうちに、奇妙な違和感がむくむくとわき上がってきて。[%p]"
msgstr "13100:But the more I looked, the more something seemed wrong.[%p]"

msgid "13200:[name]拓巳[line]「え……？」[%p]"
msgstr "13200:[name]拓巳[line]Huh?[%p]"

msgid "13300:ついには、イスから腰を浮かしてしまっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "13300:Finally, I leaned out of my chair.[%p]"

msgid "13400:[name]拓巳[line]「ちょ、ちょっとどいて……！」[%p]"
msgstr "13400:[name]拓巳[line]M-Move out of the way![%p]"

msgid "13500:[name]三住[line]「イテテ、おい、どうしたんだよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "13500:[name]三住[line]Ow! What's gotten into you?[%p]"

msgid "13600:三住くんを押しのけて、黒板に歩み寄る。[linebreak]そこに書かれている文字を見て、僕は――[%p]"
msgstr "13600:I pushed past Misumi and walked up to the blackboard. When I saw the words written there, I...[%p]"

msgid "13700:自分の心臓が、一瞬キュッと縮み上がったような錯覚に陥った。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:I felt like my heart was strangling itself in my chest.[%p]"

msgid "13800:――その目だれの目？[%p]"
msgstr "13800:Whose eyes are those?[%p]"

msgid "13900:それは、僕がよく“神の視線”を感じたときに心の中でつぶやく言葉。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:The words I always silently said to myself whenever I felt “the gaze of God.”[%p]"

msgid "14000:口外したことなんてない。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:I'd never told them to anyone else.[%p]"

msgid "14100:話す相手なんていない。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:There was no one to tell them to.[%p]"

msgid "14200:三住くんにだって話したことはない。[linebreak]このクラスで、僕がその言葉をよく使っていることを知っている人間が、いるはずない。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:Not even Misumi. Nobody in this class could possibly know that I said that phrase all the time.[%p]"

msgid "14300:どうして……[linebreak]誰が……[linebreak]なんのために……？[%p]"
msgstr "14300:Why? Who? For what reason?[%p]"

msgid "14400:とっさに振り返り、教室内を見渡す。[%p]"
msgstr "14400:I spun around and looked around the classroom.[%p]"

msgid "14500:僕の行動に注目しているのは、三住くんだけだ。[%p]"
msgstr "14500:Only Misumi was paying any attention to me.[%p]"

msgid "14600:他は、みんな思い思いに親しい友達とだべっていたり、持ち込み禁止のマンガを読んでいたり、机に突っ伏して寝ていたりとさまざま。[%p]"
msgstr "14600:Everyone else was talking to themselves, or reading manga they weren't supposed to have at school, or sleeping at their desks.[%p]"

msgid "14700:誰だ……？[linebreak]誰が、これを書いた？[linebreak]いつ、書かれたんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "14700:Who? Who wrote this? When did they do it?[%p]"

msgid "14800:“こんなのただの偶然だ”[%18]"
msgstr "14800:“It's just a coincidence.”[%18]"

msgid "14900:“これはきっと目の錯覚だ”[%18]"
msgstr "14900:“I'm hallucinating.”[%18]"

msgid "15000:“犯人はこの学園内にいる”[%18]"
msgstr "15000:“Whoever did it is inside the school.”[%18]"

msgid "15100:“僕を挑発しているんだ”[%18]"
msgstr "15100:“They're taunting me.”[%18]"

msgid "15200:“今すぐあれを消したい”[%18]"
msgstr "15200:“I want to erase it now.”[%18]"

msgid "15300:[name]三住[line]「なあ？　どうしたんだ？」[%p]"
msgstr "15300:[name]三住[line]Hello? What's gotten into you?[%p]"

msgid "15400:歩み寄ってきた三住くんが、僕の肩をつかんで揺すってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:Misumi walked up to me and grabbed me by the shoulders to shake me.[%p]"

msgid "15500:[name]三住[line]「聞いてる？」[%p]"
msgstr "15500:[name]三住[line]Are you listening?[%p]"

msgid "15600:[name]三住[line]「おーーい、タク？」[%p]"
msgstr "15600:[name]三住[line]Yo! Taku?[%p]"

msgid "15700:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "15700:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "15800:こんなの、よくある言葉だ……。[linebreak]下らない、どうでもいい落書きなんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:Every word in that phrase was commonly used. It was just some stupid scribbling.[%p]"

msgid "15900:そう思おうとしたけど、薄気味悪さを覚えて、結局、周囲の目に怯えながら、急いでその落書きを消した。[%p]"
msgstr "15900:I tried to tell myself that, but I started to feel really creeped out. In the end, I quickly erased them, hoping that nobody was watching me.[%p]"

msgid "16000:僕が教室に入ってきたときには、もうすでに書かれてたっけ？[linebreak]思い出せない……。黒板になにが書いてあるかなんて、普段はまったく意識していないし。[%p]"
msgstr "16000:Was that already on the blackboard when I'd come in? I couldn't remember. Usually, I didn't pay any attention to what was on the blackboard.[%p]"

msgid "16100:[name]三住[line]「なあ？　どうしたんだ？」[%p]"
msgstr "16100:[name]三住[line]Hello? What's gotten into you?[%p]"

msgid "16200:歩み寄ってきた三住くんが、僕の肩をつかんで揺すってくる。[%p]"
msgstr "16200:Misumi walked up to me and grabbed me by the shoulders to shake me.[%p]"

msgid "16300:[name]三住[line]「聞いてる？」[%p]"
msgstr "16300:[name]三住[line]Are you listening?[%p]"

msgid "16400:[name]三住[line]「おーーい、タク？」[%p]"
msgstr "16400:[name]三住[line]Yo! Taku?[%p]"

msgid "16500:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "16500:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "16600:だ、誰が書いたものだろうと、僕にはきっと関係ないさ。[linebreak]ただの偶然に決まってる……。[linebreak]こんなの、よくある言葉だ……。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:I-It didn't matter who'd written them. It was just a coincidence. People used these words all the time.[%p]"

msgid "16700:下らない、どうでもいい落書きなんだ……。[linebreak]きっと、そうだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "16700:It was just some stupid scribbling. Yeah... just some stupid scribbling.[%p]"

msgid "16800:そう思い込もうとしたけど、やっぱりどうしてもソワソワしてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "16800:I tried to tell myself that, but I was still really scared.[%p]"

msgid "16900:誰があれを書いたのかは、結局分からずじまいだった。できればクラスの全員に聞いて回りたかったけど、そんな勇気もなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "16900:I never did figure out who'd written them. I wanted to go around the class and ask, but I didn't have the courage.[%p]"

msgid "17000:そうこうしているうちにホームルームが始まっちゃって、あの落書きは“誰だ〜、落書きしたヤツは〜”という担任の言葉とともにあっさりと消されてしまった。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:Before long, homeroom began. The teacher came in and asked, “Who wrote this on the blackboard?” He sounded annoyed, and erased them.[%p]"

msgid "17100:なんとなく薄気味悪さみたいなものを感じたけど、あえていつも通りを心がけることにする。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:It was really creepy, but I decided I was going to force myself to behave normally.[%p]"

msgid "17200:ヘタに怯えたりしたら、あれが僕と関係があるなんらかのメッセージだって認めちゃうことになるから。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:If I let myself seem scared, I'd just be admitting the message had something to do with me.[%p]"

msgid "17300:そんなわけはないんだ。あれは単なる偶然だ。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:And it didn't, okay? It was just a coincidence.[%p]"

msgid "17400:何度も何度も自分にそう言い聞かせながら、僕は予定通り、学校帰りに行きつけのネットカフェへと向かった。[%p]"
msgstr "17400:I kept telling myself that, over and over, until it was time for me to go to a net café after school, just like I'd planned to do.[%p]"

msgid "17500:『＠カフェ』は、外出嫌いの僕が唯一来るアミューズメントスポットだ。[%p]"
msgstr "17500:The café 's name was @Café. It was the one place I liked going.[%p]"

msgid "17600:渋谷のセンター街沿いにあって、ＤＱＮっぽい三次元女とか冴えないサラリーマンなどの客が多いけど、全室個室だから無問題。[%p]"
msgstr "17600:It was along Center Street in Shibuya. There were a lot of loser salarymen and DQN 3D girls here, but you got your own personal room, so it didn't matter.[%p]"

msgid "17700:ちなみに今いる個室――ＲＯＯＭ３７――は僕の指定席と化していて、店内でも一番奥まったところにある。[%p]"
msgstr "17700:The room I was in, room 37, was kind of my personal spot. It was the one furthest back in the café.[%p]"

msgid "17800:飲み放題のジュースを取りに行くには不便だけど、近くの席にあまり人が入らないから比較的静かなんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "17800:It sucked when you wanted to go get some of the free soda, but it was relatively quiet because not many people came by.[%p]"

msgid "17900:週に一度か二度、学校帰りにわざわざここに寄る理由は、エンスーに別のＩＤでログインするため。[%p]"
msgstr "17900:I would always come here once or twice a week on my way home from school, so that I could log into ESO under a different ID.[%p]"

msgid "18000:要するに息抜きかな。ナイトハルトは名前が知られすぎちゃってるんだよね。[%p]"
msgstr "18000:It was my way of relaxing. KnightHeart was too well known, you see.[%p]"

msgid "18100:悪い気分じゃないけど、さすがに毎日毎日英雄として模範的行動を繰り返しているのもストレスがたまるものなのさ。[%p]"
msgstr "18100:I enjoyed being famous, but having to be the hero everyone looked up to all the time was stressful.[%p]"

msgid "18200:というわけでこうして別[color index="A0FF0000"]アバター[color index="800000"]を作ってプレイしてるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "18200:That's why I liked to play with a different [color index="A0FF0000"]avatar[color index="800000"] sometimes.[%p]"

msgid "18300:こっちで使ってるのは『リーゼロッテ』っていう女キャラ。[linebreak]ただ、リーゼロッテの戦歴は今ひとつパッとしない。徹底して引き立て役をやらせているからね。[%p]"
msgstr "18300:This character was a girl. Her name was Liselotte. Liselotte didn't really have many big accomplishments to her name, though. Whenever I played as her, I made sure other characters got the glory.[%p]"

msgid "18400:今日も３時間ほどまったりプレイしてストレスを発散した。その後しばらく、[color index="A0FF0000"]ギルド[color index="800000"]の仲間とチャットで下らない話やエロい話で盛り上がった。[%p]"
msgstr "18400:I worked out some stress by playing for three hours. Just grinding, never really doing any hard content. Then I talked about dumb stuff, and some naughty stuff, with the rest of my [color index="A0FF0000"]guild[color index="800000"].[%p]"

msgid "18500:店を出たときには、夜の９時になろうとしていた。[%p]"
msgstr "18500:By the time I left the café, it was almost 9:00 PM.[%p]"

msgid "18600:この時間帯のセンター街は、特にＤＱＮが多い。[%p]"
msgstr "18600:Center Street at this hour was filled with DQNs.[%p]"

msgid "18700:道のあちこちに我が物顔で座り込み、下品な笑い声をあげながらファーストフードのハンバーガーを食べている連中を見ると、反吐が出そうになる。[%p]"
msgstr "18700:They would sit on the sidewalk like they owned the place, eating fast food and laughing in their disgusting voices. It made me want to vomit.[%p]"

msgid "18800:ヘタに目を合わしたら、あのバカどもはすぐに反応して攻撃してくるし。とことん野蛮だ。[%p]"
msgstr "18800:And if you made eye contact with them, they'd get mad and attack you. They were barbarians.[%p]"

msgid "18900:あんなの人間じゃない。雄と雌だよ。社会的知性の欠片もないね。[linebreak]あんな連中は死ね。氏ねじゃなくて死ね。[%p]"
msgstr "18900:No, they weren't even human. They were worse than that. They were animals. They didn't have a shred of common social decency or intelligence. I wished they would all just die. I meant it, too. It wasn't something I was just saying.[%p]"

msgid "19000:とは思いつつも、結局のところ相手をするだけ無駄なんだよね。僕は無駄なことはしない。だから急いでセンター街を離脱する。[%p]"
msgstr "19000:But you know... just dealing with them was a waste of time. And I wasn't the kind of guy to waste time. So I quickly left Center Street.[%p]"

msgid "19100:『＠カフェ』を出たら、近くにある『まんがだらけ』か、少し遠回りになるけど『アニメエイト』のどちらかに寄るのが僕の定番コースだ。[%p]"
msgstr "19100:After leaving @Café, I would always stop at either the nearby Mangadarake, or the animeight that was a little further away.[%p]"

msgid "19200:今日は『アニメエイト』に行くことに決め、駅の南口へ向かった。[%p]"
msgstr "19200:Today I decided to go to animeight, and headed for the station's south entrance.[%p]"

msgid "19300:こっち側に来るとＤＱＮの数は一気に減る。[%p]"
msgstr "19300:There were far fewer DQNs here.[%p]"

msgid "19400:ホント、センター街はカオスだ。あそこを歩くだけで息苦しささえ覚える。可能なら一歩たりとも近づきたくない。[%p]"
msgstr "19400:Really, Center Street was pure chaos. Just walking through there made it hard to breathe. If I could've, I would've rather never gone there at all.[%p]"

msgid "19500:『＠カフェ』と『まんがだらけ』だけ残して滅びてほしいよ。[%p]"
msgstr "19500:I wished they'd just tear the whole place down, leaving only @Café and Mangadarake.[%p]"

msgid "19600:さてと、今日もコミックや同人誌を物色していこう。[%p]"
msgstr "19600:Anyway, it was time to look at some manga and dojinshi.[%p]"

msgid "19700:あ、そういえばブラチューのＤＶＤ５巻って予約受付がそろそろ始まるんじゃなかったっけ。[%p]"
msgstr "19700:Oh, and Blood Tune's 5th DVD was probably about to go up for pre-order.[%p]"

